## 🗂️ Data Model (παράδειγμα)
```go
type Artist struct {
    ID           int
    Name         string
    Image        string
    Members      []string
    CreationYear int
    FirstAlbum   time.Time
}

type Gig struct {
    ArtistID  int
    Location  string
    Date      time.Time
}

💻 Σελίδες & UI

    Artists list: responsive cards (εικόνα, όνομα, έτος, first album) + search bar + filters.

    Artist detail: εικόνα, μέλη, πίνακας με (date, location).

    Locations: table [location | #artists | #gigs] με link σε filtered λίστα.

    Dashboard: counts (artists, members, locations), μικρό chart με vanilla JS/Canvas.

⚡ Event/Action

    Live search: typing → fetch('/api/suggest?q=...') → autocomplete → update DOM.

    Manual refresh: κουμπί → POST /api/refresh → re-download data → UI toast.

🛡️ Error Handling

    Να μην κάνει crash ποτέ: recover middleware.

    Validation στα query params.

    “No results” states.

    Timeouts/retries στο API fetch.

✅ Tests

    Unit: JSON parsing, date parsing, normalization, search filtering.

    Handler tests: httptest για /api/search, /artists/{id}, 404.

    Index tests: correctness & case-insensitive lookups.

